overview: A-ha - Norwegian music band formed in 1983 in Oslo. a-ha - one of the leading groups of electro-pop style, which appeared on the decline of the "new wave". Music a-ha inherent graphically, some coolish ("Nordic") style, synth-guitar sound, expressive ballad melodies coupled with unobtrusive dance music, romantic, sometimes full of slight sadness, mood.
title: A-ha - Video Collection (1984-2010) Vol.1
